722366f-a.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 90th Street
722366f-a.text:
1112 Park Avenue, on S.W. corner of 90th Street, newly completed,
replacing two 5-story buildings. In 1930 the 7-story double
apartment house (Meteor) on the N.W. corner of 89th Street
will be replaced by a 17-story building, but the two little
houses in between will stay.
1927.
Knickerbocker Photo Service.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
